  "titles": "Word Bearers Procurators with Jump Packs",
  "lore": "Although the Order of the Procurators, or the Vor Nergeth as they were known within their Legion, took to war adorned with the helix symbol of the Apothecarion it would transpire that their efforts would not be concentrated on the preservation of Legionaries, but instead on seeking to desecrate the bodies of the fallen, harvesting their organs even as they suffered the last agonising throes of life. Such gross defilement served to fuel dark rituals of summoning and reanimation, bringing forth the denizens of the Warp, and imbuing themselves and their apprentices with the stolen lifeforce of their victims.",
